title: Banners posted on the downtown Cairo KFC
description: Photographer's description: Pictures taken during the Egyptian Revolution. Text in image:  عاوز انترنت- ارحل، خلى عندك دم VATTENE MUBARAK. Translation of Text in image: I want internet -  LEAVE, Have some blood in you. GO MUBĀRAK.
